<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>ChoreQuest — Offline</title>
    <style>
      /* All styles are inline — external CSS cannot load when offline */
      *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

      body {
        font-family: ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
        background: linear-gradient(to bottom right, #ffffff, #eff6ff, #dbeafe);
        min-height: 100vh;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        text-align: center;
        padding: 2rem;
      }

      .card {
        background: white;
        border-radius: 1.25rem;
        box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
        padding: 3rem 2rem;
        max-width: 380px;
        width: 100%;
      }

      .logo {
        width: 72px;
        height: 72px;
        background: linear-gradient(to bottom right, #3b82f6, #a855f7);
        border-radius: 14px;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        font-size: 1.75rem;
        font-weight: 800;
        color: white;
        margin: 0 auto 1.5rem;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.3);
      }

      h1 {
        font-size: 1.5rem;
        font-weight: 800;
        color: #111827;
        margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
        letter-spacing: -0.02em;
      }

      p {
        color: #6b7280;
        line-height: 1.6;
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
        font-size: 0.95rem;
      }

      button {
        background: #3b82f6;
        color: white;
        border: none;
        padding: 0.75rem 2rem;
        border-radius: 9999px;
        font-size: 1rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        cursor: pointer;
        transition: background 0.15s ease;
        box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.35);
      }

      button:hover { background: #2563eb; }
      button:active { background: #1d4ed8; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="card">
      <div class="logo">CQ</div>
      <h1>You're Offline</h1>
      <p>ChoreQuest needs an internet connection to load your chores and tokens. Check your connection and try again.</p>
      <button onclick="window.location.reload()">Try Again</button>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
